('スターバックス', 'cafe', 35.6491519, 139.6927215, 'osm', 'osm:way/621235316', 'https://www.openstreetmap.org/way/621235316', '15309942 東京都 目黒区 23', '+81-3-6417-0202', 'https://starbucks.co.jp/roastery', '{"osm_type":"way","osm_id":621235316,"tags":{"addr:block_number":"19","addr:city":"目黒区","addr:housenumber":"23","addr:neighbourhood":"青葉台二丁目","addr:postcode":"15309942","addr:province":"東京都","alt_name:en":"Starbucks Reserve Roastery Tokyo","amenity":"cafe","bar":"yes","branch":"リザーブ ロースタリー","branch:en":"Reserve Roastery Tokyo","brand":"スターバックス","brand:en":"Starbucks","brand:ja":"スターバックス","brand:wikidata":"Q37158","brand:wikipedia":"en:Starbucks Reserve","building":"yes","building:levels":"4","building:levels:underground":"1","check_date":"2025-09-15","contact:instagram":"https://instagram.com/starbucksreserve_tokyo;https://instagram.com/explore/locations/1961080280637489","contact:tripadvisor":"https://tripadvisor.com/Restaurant_Review-g1066450-d16714835-Reviews-or15-Starbucks_Reserve_R_Roastery_Tokyo-Meguro_Tokyo_Tokyo_Prefecture_Kanto.html","contact:yelp":"https://yelp.com/biz/starbucks-reserve-roastery-tokyo-meguro","cuisine":"coffee_shop","description:en":"World’s second largest Starbucks as of 2025, a four-story 32,000 sq ft roastery with largest coffee cask, extensive tea bar, and cherry blossom views along Meguro River. Designed by Kengo Kuma, blending coffee craft with Japanese culture.","description:es":"Segundo Starbucks más grande del mundo en 2025, tostadero de 4 pisos con 3,000 m², el barril de café más grande, gran bar de té y vistas de cerezos en flor en el río Meguro. Diseñado por Kengo Kuma, combinando arte del café y cultura japonesa.","description:fr":"Deuxième plus grand Starbucks au monde en 2025, brûlerie de 4 étages de 3 000 m² avec grande cuve à café, vaste bar à thé et vue sur cerisiers en fleurs le long de rivière Meguro. Conçu par Kengo Kuma, alliant savoir-faire du café et culture japonaise.","description:ja":"2025年時点で世界で2番目に大きいスターバックス。4階建て、約3000平方メートルの焙煎所で、最大のコーヒータンク、充実したティーバー、目黒川沿いの桜の景色を備える。隈研吾設計で、コーヒー技術と日本文化を融合。","description:ko":"2025년 기준 세계에서 두 번째로 큰 스타벅스, 4층 규모 약 3,000㎡ 로스터리, 가장 큰 커피 저장 탱크, 풍부한 차 바, 메구로 강 벚꽃 경관 포함. 겐고 쿠마 설계, 커피 기술과 일본 문화 융합.","description:zh":"截至2025年，全球第二大星巴克，四层楼，约3000平方米的烘焙工厂，拥有最大的咖啡储罐，丰富的茶吧，以及目黑川沿岸的樱花景观。由隈研吾设计，融合咖啡工艺与日本文化。","designer":"Kengo Kuma","dog":"yes","internet_access":"wlan","name":"スターバックス","name:en":"Starbucks","name:ja":"スターバックス","official_name":"スターバックスコーヒー","official_name:en":"Starbucks Coffee","official_name:ja":"スターバックスコーヒー","opening_hours":"07:00-22:00","outdoor_seating":"yes","payment:au_pay":"yes","payment:cash":"yes","payment:credit_cards":"yes","payment:d_barai":"yes","payment:debit_cards":"yes","payment:kessai":"yes","payment:nfc":"yes","payment:nfc_mobile_payments":"yes","payment:pasmo":"yes","payment:paypay":"yes","payment:rakuten_pay":"yes","payment:suica":"yes","payment:transit_cards":"yes","payment:v_money":"yes","phone":"+81-3-6417-0202","source":"local knowledge","takeaway":"yes","toilets":"yes","toilets:wheelchair":"designated","website":"https://starbucks.co.jp/roastery","website:design":"https://starbucksreserve.com/locations/tokyo/highlights","website:menu":"https://product.starbucks.co.jp/s/?purchase_methods=RESERVE_ROASTERY_TOKYO&category_code=beverage","wheelchair":"yes","wikidata":"Q65665536","wikimedia_commons":"Category:Starbucks Reserve Roastery Tokyo","wikipedia":"ja:スターバックス リザーブ ロースタリー 東京"},"importer":"overpass-japan-seed-v1"}'::jsonb, null, null),
